rows.label: qst202512_msg0001
rows.name:
KOS-MOS Re:! Are you okay?!
Are you hurt anywhere?

rows.label: qst202512_msg0002
rows.name:
Yes, I am fine. Are
you unhurt, Astelle?

rows.label: qst202512_msg0003
rows.name: Yes! I'm fine!

rows.label: qst202512_msg0004
rows.name:
KOS-MOS Re: protected me,
so I'm not hurt at all.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0005
rows.name: I see. I am glad...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202512_msg0006
rows.name: Um...[ML:Dash ] KOS-MOS Re:, I'm sorry!

rows.label: qst202512_msg0007
rows.name:
It's because of my selfishness
that you had to go through this.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0008
rows.name: I didn't mean for this to happen.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0009
rows.name:
Please do not concern yourself.
Protecting you is my mission.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0010
rows.name: But...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202512_msg0011
rows.name: Well, do you understand now?

rows.label: qst202512_msg0012
rows.name:
Selfishness can put your friends
and comrades in danger.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0013
rows.name:
Now that you've learned your lesson,
don't ever say you want to come
to a place like this again.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0014
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]Yes... everyone, I'm truly sorry!

rows.label: qst202512_msg0015
rows.name:
That's enough now. You had
a scare too, Astelle.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0016
rows.name:
If you understand, then
that's all that matters.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0017
rows.name:
More importantly, did you get
what you were looking for?

rows.label: qst202512_msg0018
rows.name: Yes...[ML:Dash ] It's this.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0019
rows.name: Is this...[ML:Dash ] some kind of machine part?

rows.label: qst202512_msg0020
rows.name: Yes.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0021
rows.name: Um...[ML:Dash ] KOS-MOS Re:.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0022
rows.name:
When we get back to Luxuria,
I'd like you to bear with me
for just a little longer...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202512_msg0023
rows.name: Is that okay?

rows.label: qst202512_msg0024
rows.name: You still haven't learned your lesson?

rows.label: qst202512_msg0025
rows.name:
No, it's not that. There's something
I want to give to KOS-MOS Re:.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0026
rows.name:
That's why I want you
to come to my room.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0027
rows.name:
I won't cause any more
trouble, so please!

rows.label: qst202512_msg0028
rows.name: What do we do, Zeke?

rows.label: qst202512_msg0029
rows.name: Well, I suppose that much is fine...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202512_msg0030
rows.name: Really! Thank you, onii-chan!

rows.label: qst202512_msg0031
rows.name:
You really only act cute
at times like this.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0032
rows.name: Are you fine with it too, KOS-MOS Re:?

rows.label: qst202512_msg0033
rows.name: Yes, there is no problem.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0034
rows.name: Then let's hurry back to Luxuria.

rows.label: qst202512_msg0035
rows.name:
My room is in the Hall of
Reception, so I'll see you there!
